Controlled via the 4.3-inch color capacitive touchscreen inset into the left front corner – which requires a somewhat firmer touch than the average smartphone, we found, though the UI is straightforward and easy to follow – a double-tap on the display automatically powers the worksurface between whatever sitting and standing presets you’ve established (a subsequent tap stops it mid-movement).
